text: Lucie Cesca (born 26 November 1994) is a French water polo player. She was a member of the France women's national water polo team at the 2015 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * lucie-cesca France waterpolo * nee-a-troyes-lucie-cesca Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:French water polo players Category:People from Troyes Category:Sportspeople from Grand Est
